name: NewHampshirePoliticalBriefing
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: NH Political Briefing sends current political news to your Alexa app, and is read aloud in your Flash Briefing by Alexa. Content is curated from sources around the web. Just enable the skill, and then ask Alexa to give you a "Flash Briefing." Or, ask Alexa "What's in the news?" Brought to you by CustomScripts. Source feed: http://customscripts.tech/category/nh-politics/feed/
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
